songs.title: But How*
songs.lyrics:
Now I'm up whoa whoa
I ain't growl I need it right now
This ain't a song this me thinking out loud
I really love your smile
I'm obsessed, but how?
I will never put you down
I would rather love you down
You got me in the hot seat now
Feeling like an animal baby
I'll eat you like a cannibal baby
